{"tid":1974450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"送口罩利誘交選民登記表 反對派同鄉會：我哋都要交數！","createTime":"2020-04-16T00:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T08:41:50.000Z","uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e87450bde3790e5b995bcd4f12185251d307ff3","tid":1974450,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T00:34:36.000Z","msg":"反對派衞星組織為求選民登記「交數」，不惜以口罩利誘。網傳由「香港東莞橫瀝同鄉會」寄出的口罩相片，信封內夾附選民登記表，並指若填妥並寄回表格，就可額外獲得5個口罩。《蘋果》佯裝該會會員致電，職員承認此事，指要就登記選民「交數」；收到該照片的職工盟主席吳敏兒表示，同鄉會顯然以抗疫做幌子，過度收集市民的個人資料，質疑若只是推動選民登記，「點解要用口罩嚟換？」<br />\n<br />\n今年立法會選舉預計在9月初舉行，新選民登記截止日期為5月2日，即尚餘約半個月時間，因此各陣營也最後衝刺爭取支持者登記成為選民。吳敏兒近日收到朋友傳送的照片，顯示「香港東莞橫瀝同鄉會有限公司」信封裝有口罩，並附有紙條，指若會員填妥及寄回夾附的選民登記表，便可額外獲得5個口罩。記者佯裝該會會員致電，職員承認此事，指原定派發5個口罩，由於登記人數過多，改為每人派發3個，若寄回填妥表格「我哋會長就另外買多5個口罩畀你。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200416/W5QB23NWJJSIWIY2JIYRHTE5JA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200416%2FW5QB23NWJJSIWIY2JIYRHTE5JA%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=67d52ebe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200416%2FW5QB23NWJJSIWIY2JIYRHTE5JA%2F&h=1f809060\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200416/W5QB23NWJJSIWIY2JIYRHTE5JA/</a>"},{"pid":"110a4033bc495a1d3f9222417f8ee0661590e717","tid":1974450,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T00:36:24.000Z","msg":"本文重點：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">26-55歲選民登記人數唔夠七成</span></span></strong><br />\n選民登記填表機 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><a href=\"http://hk2020.vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=969d2887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk2020.vote</a></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g8kyKnb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg8kyKnb.png&h=20d302ba&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n由於冇18-20歲嘅人口數字 我就計唔到18-20歲手足個登記率<br />\n如果有高人指教希望可以fill番粒數<br />\n但係 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">26-55歲呢30年嘅選民登記人數 都唔夠七成</span></span></strong><br />\n係全世界都要呼籲所有人做選民 <br />\n唔只係後生仔<br />\n要知道去換身分證其實有<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">選管會Purple姐姐/哥哥比表登記</span></span></span></strong><br />\n其實多數都會填 當然都仲會有人唔填<br />\n但係 重點係 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">26-55歲選民登記人數唔夠七成</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要呼籲<span style=\"color: violet;\">全世界都登記做選民</span> 係全世界</span></strong><br />\n上 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><a href=\"http://hk2020.vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=969d2887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk2020.vote</a></span></strong> 逐步逐步填 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">5分鐘就搞掂架啦</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nSource: 如你是我 巴打"},{"pid":"51dcf88c01bd2c831cca42923614cb42b00698bd","tid":1974450,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T00:38:38.000Z","msg":"算唔算貪污<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f299be05cf3f7373117486f852e0df1ce359404e","tid":1974450,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51dcf88c01bd2c831cca42923614cb42b00698bd","tid":1974450,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T00:38:38.000Z","msg":"算唔算貪污<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T00:40:03.000Z","msg":"有間接利益就算"},{"pid":"736e28fcec9584704efca9593a273e8107244d2d","tid":1974450,"uid":76591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T00:41:30.000Z","msg":"登記咗你D口罩我一定要投你保皇黨架咩<img src=\"/as